text: Duncan de Moor (born 11 April 1994), professionally known as Duncan Laurence, is a Dutch singer who representend the Netherlands at the Eurovision Song Contest 2019 in Tel Aviv, Israel with the song "Arcade" from the album Loving You Is a Losing Game and won the contest. Laurence was born in Spijkenisse and is bisexual. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Bisexual people Category:Dutch LGBT people Category:Dutch singer- songwriters Category:Eurovision Song Contest winners Category:LGBT singers Category:Musicians from South Holland Category:People from South Holland
